---
---
<section class="py-16 bg-white border-b border-brand-border/30">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Configure Products, Offers and Access Clearly</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-textMain">We manage the relationship between your content and how customers purchase and access it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-brand-softBg rounded-xl p-8 border border-brand-border/50">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3">Product</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-textMain mb-6 italic">The learning experience, content or program the customer receives.</p>

        <p class="text-brand-textMain mb-4">We structure and configure relevant Kajabi Products, including:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-brand-textMain font-medium">
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Courses</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Coaching</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Communities</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Podcasts</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Downloads</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-softBg rounded-xl p-8 border border-brand-border/50">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-secondary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3">Offer</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-textMain mb-6 italic">The commercial package connecting Products with pricing and customer access.</p>

        <p class="text-brand-textMain mb-4">We set up the commercial pathways, configuring:</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-brand-textMain font-medium text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-primary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Product packaging</div>
          <div class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-primary rounded-full mr-2"></span> One-time pricing</div>
          <div class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-primary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Payment plans</div>
          <div class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-primary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Subscriptions</div>
          <div class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-primary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Access duration</div>
          <div class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-primary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Offer descriptions</div>
          <div class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-primary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Included Products</div>
          <div class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-primary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Coupons & terms</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 text-sm text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p>Options depend on Kajabi’s current features and your client plan restrictions. Payment options may depend on your configured payment processor and location. TheEduAssist configures the available options but does not act as the payment processor.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
